source.query:
select SF_LOAD_TS_EST, RECORD_CONTENT from "MOBILITYCORELOCAL"."MSLOGS"."STREAM_SMF_FEDERATE_PROD"
where RECORD_CONTENT:tags.appName IN ( select * from "MOBILITYCORELOCAL"."MSLOGS"."SMF_APPNAMES") OR RECORD_CONTENT:tags.job = 'pfcp'

select SF_LOAD_TS_EST, RECORD_CONTENT from "MOBILITYCORELOCAL"."MSLOGS"."STREAM_UPF_FEDERATE_PROD"
where RECORD_CONTENT:tags.appName IN ( select * from "MOBILITYCORELOCAL"."MSLOGS"."UPF_APPNAMES")
